file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0

info:
  version: 3.0.0
  title: DLTS API

servers:
  - url: /api/v2

paths:
  /:
    get:
      summary: Get API info
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
  /openapi.yaml:
    get:
      summary: Get API document
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
  /clusters/:clusterId/teams/:teamId/jobs:
    get:
      summary: Get jobs of spefied cluster & team
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
  /clusters/:clusterId/jobs/:jobId:
    get:
      summary: Get spefied job
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
